IDataBindingsAccessor Interface

Definition

Allows access to the collection of data-binding expressions on a control at design time.

In this Article

public interface IDataBindingsAccessor

Properties

DataBindings

Gets a collection of all data bindings on the control. This property is read-only.

public System.Web.UI.DataBindingCollection DataBindings { get; }
Value
DataBindingCollection

The collection of data bindings.

HasDataBindings

Gets a value indicating whether the control contains any data-binding logic.

public bool HasDataBindings { get; }
Value
Boolean

true if the control contains data binding logic.
